THREAT: WX - A NW-SE BAND OF BKN TO OVC LOW CLOUDS OVER THE KAUAI CHANNEL HAS EMBD TOWERING CU WITH TOPS NEAR 25K FT, WITH POTENTIAL FOR ISOLATED THUNDERSTORMS WITH TOPS NEAR 35K FT. AIRMET SIERRA IN EFFECT FOR KAUAI & OAHU. IMPROVING CONDS ARE EXPECTED OVER KAUAI THIS AFTERNOON. THIS BAND WILL STALL AND GRADUALLY DISSIPATE NEAR OAHU/MOLOKAI OVERNIGHT.
